snippet.title: Echo Generation  - Official Reveal Trailer [4K 60fps]
snippet.description:
Echo Generation is a turn-based adventure game about a gang of kids investigating supernatural occurrences while battling monsters and mechs to save their hometown. 
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1072300/Echo_Generation

Coming 2021 to Xbox Series X, Xbox One and Steam.
